<div class="story"> <p>Duck Landing is an oceanfront subdivision in the heart of downtown Duck consisting of 53 building lots situated on either side of Duck Land Lane. There is an active home owners association which maintains the clubhouse, indoor pool, tennis court, ocean access and the private road. All of the lots are already built on and most of the homes have an in ground pool. You can find Duck Landing just past the subdivision of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/poteskeet.asp" title="Poteskeet">Poteskeet</a> as you travel north on Rt 12 and just before you get to <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/schooner-ridge.asp" title="Schooner Ridge">Schooner Ridge</a>. </p> 
